The paper deals with the problem of building sparse brain networks at voxel level, which involves optimization and analysis of large-scale data. This suggests that the paper may belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE), social and information networks (cs.SI), computer vision and pattern recognition (cs.CV), and multimedia (cs.MM).
